Francis D. John, 35-year-old president, will assume the additional job of chief executive officer.
He succeeds Paul J. Montle, 42, who will remain chairman.
National Environmental also said it will move its headquarters from Hingham to Folcroft, Pa., the site of its sludge dewatering facility.
National Environmental, formerly Yankee Cos., is a sludge treatment company. 

